{"tid":1010960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港獨聯以死相搏執垃圾唔搞暴動 清潔工依然做到無停手？","createTime":"2019-02-06T11:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T12:20:01.000Z","uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6cf1a404ee8d4f96704162015d315af7858e04","tid":1010960,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkgpao.com/articles/255033?fbclid=IwAR1NDiJ-0skIwA0MULzIMwmJWqzOk1aNDgJKKf2HrZ1nStDoQtUvim2VQaY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkgpao.com%2Farticles%2F255033%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1NDiJ-0skIwA0MULzIMwmJWqzOk1aNDgJKKf2HrZ1nStDoQtUvim2VQaY&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=69827618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkgpao.com/articles/255033?fbclid=IwAR1NDiJ-0skIwA0MULzIMwmJWqzOk1aNDgJKKf2HrZ1nStDoQtUvim2VQaY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLqeuGK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLqeuGK.jpg&h=a10fb8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n一班獨友早前揚言延續旺暴「義士」精神，點知去到旺角夜市時，見到警方重兵駐守，即刻淆晒底，話自己係嚟執垃圾保持地方清潔（請按此重溫）。你以為成班獨友「義士」變「義工」咁好心？但似乎佢哋做戲並冇做足全套，因為翌日有清潔工表示，夜市留低一地垃圾同食物殘渣，做到冇停手喎，說好執垃圾的獨友們呢？<br />\n[\\red]<br />\n料初二清晨垃圾更多<br />\n大年初一早上，旺角一班清潔工忙於清理前一晚夜市所遺留的垃圾，據香港01報道，今年嘅清潔人手增加咗，但依然做唔停手，當中有清潔工批評香港市民缺乏公德心，食物殘渣四圍擺又唔包好，搞到啲汁漏晒出嚟，並估計初二清晨會有更多垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n[red]<br />\n<br />\n明明獨友話幫手執垃圾，點解旺角仲係一地垃圾？到底班獨友係得把口，定係粗心大意執唔晒，就不得而知喇。依家獨友明知咁多執法人員駐守旺角，唔知仲敢唔敢出去「執垃圾」呢？<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4c8469be0822e6447cdea0c9d8bc14f91f8e862b","tid":1010960,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"寧為<span style=\"color: red;\">肉</span>碎 以死傷<span style=\"color: red;\">掃</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rnbMdP6SEe.AA_Paz7YIjg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/hk01_725/206a5d7cd460cd13082300dee075ba8a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu